				<title>Measurements are off</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13816392/scp-5585#post-4863228</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 05 Jan 2021 22:49:34 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Seraph72</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>7186954</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Your metric conversions are off. It is growing 150cm a week, which is a meter and half. It is 4.6 kilometers in, or in other words 4600 meters. In 8 months, it will be 32x1.5 meters in radius (48m), but still only 1% of the way to the door.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
